    • Method Detail

      • code

        int code()
        All error codes are defined as static final in WeemoError This allows you to switch across all possible errors and have one method to rule them all!

        Please note that these error codes are NOT CONSTANT across SDK version and may change. You should not save or replicate their value.
        Returns:
        The error code
